Roast Pork with sharp provolone and broccoli rabe Yes, there was a line that wrapped around however they have an efficient system and it moves fast. Yes, they take CC Yes, finding seats can be a bit tough and the sandwich isn't necessarily cheap ($10+) but yes it was worth it. The fresh meat with salty cheese and slightly bitter broccoli rabe all housed in bread with the right amount of chewiness worked wonderfully. Simple/top quality ingredients.
